{"tid":1576882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母813機場又有義士被控暴動仲唔畀保釋！","createTime":"2019-09-17T12:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T07:03:40.000Z","uid":2429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1761406829d41658dd4968e9f27bf914292baf92","tid":1576882,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"多名示威者東區法院提堂　聲援者眾　等逾四小時送囚車離去<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kNnBIA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kNnBIA&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=4e20b40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kNnBIA</a><br />\n<br />\n多名因參與反送中運動而被捕的示威者，今天在東區裁判法院提堂，其中<br />\n周日（15日）北角一帶有懷疑「福建幫」人士與市民及示威者毆鬥，其中一名被警方壓在地上制服、血流披面後再被近距離施放胡椒噴劑、身穿「岳」字灰衣示威者陳以晉（19歲），被控一項襲警及一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器，獲准以 1 萬元現金保釋，但須遵守每晚 10 時至翌日早上 6 時宵禁令、不得進入案發一帶範圍、每星期一次到警署報到、不得離開香港及要交出所有旅遊證件等。案件將押後六星期至 10 月 29 日下午再訊。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">男子葉文亮（23歲）因涉於今年 8 月 13 日在機場襲擊拔槍警員黃耀華，被控一項暴動罪及一項對他人身體加以嚴重傷害罪</span>，控方於庭上表示，閉路電視攝得一名與葉文亮衣著相同的男子曾襲擊黃耀華，形容本案證據充分。控方又透露，警方從葉家中搜出波子、保鮮紙、彈叉、電筒、頭盔等物品，認為他有能力獲取該些物品，顯示他有重犯風險。<span style=\"color: red;\">法庭最終拒絕葉文亮保釋，需要還柙，案件押後至下月 28 日再訊。</span><br />\n<br />\n不少聲援者在今天二時許已到法院外聲援，陳以晉保釋離去後，繼續法院外等候接載葉文亮的囚車離開。<br />\n<br />\n傍晚近6時半，一囚車離開時，群眾不斷喊「義士加油」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義士頂住呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f67afdb21e6e47b266d7593f0a7a5723acf44c","tid":1576882,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8609c860d486a17c19c3b913f21bab61441e4e","tid":1576882,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"【極重要】（被？）自殺的失蹤人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55af1ab7fffb0c4518c2b4f2cfc769aba3cf529f","tid":1576882,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388d281ccb3fe4014247f751298d94f996345b32","tid":1576882,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa58f902e3b17b5ab9889010b164b766c5c279c7","tid":1576882,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"一定要執屋"},{"pid":"a6123d221d64652f4fa5f1199f6743881df953ae","tid":1576882,"uid":295795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:29:07.000Z","msg":"你老母推隻狗兩下救人叫加以嚴重傷害<br />\n九龍灣隻肥系廢中打到黑帶手足暈左叫普通襲擊罪<br />\n乜撚野司法公正？乜撚野法治？"},{"pid":"ff17dfa94ece8a62afd8000d7131e928c2f27969","tid":1576882,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6123d221d64652f4fa5f1199f6743881df953ae","tid":1576882,"uid":295795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:29:07.000Z","msg":"你老母推隻狗兩下救人叫加以嚴重傷害<br />\n九龍灣隻肥系廢中打到黑帶手足暈左叫普通襲擊罪<br />\n乜撚野司法公正？乜撚野法治？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"仲有撚法治咩！班狗想點就點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795769abc0331e39f50c96ada8d7fd2f10c221b0","tid":1576882,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa58f902e3b17b5ab9889010b164b766c5c279c7","tid":1576882,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"一定要執屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019